name: Emmanuella
description:
I am very faithful, sincere, considerate, passionate and kind-hearted.I have a good temper. I have many good friends in my daily life. I always get along well with family and my friends. I want to bring you happiness to the man I love. I want to find an honest, kind, passionate, responsible, naughty, passionate man to be my beloved soulmate.
I am looking for a man, who can love with all his love. Who is passionate and open to his woman, who is romantic and can accept the stream of tender feelings from me. I am very giving in relations and I want to meet man, who can take all my love and save it with tender.
